<img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Separation of Church and State</span><hr size=1> I can still remember learning about the separation of church and state in the eighth grade.  I remember thinking that it was a fabulous idea because I felt as a member of a religious minority I needed the protection of the first amendment. <br>
